OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FThe Disasters Emergency Committee
OL,7,F(DEC) has launched an urgent appeal to
OL,8,Fraise funds to reach the millions of
OL,9,Fpeople affected by twin earthquakes in
OL,10,FVenezuela.
OL,12,FThe DEC brings together 15 leading aid
OL,13,Fcharities at times of crisis overseas,
OL,14,Fand 14 of those are responding to the
OL,15,Fhumanitarian crisis in Venezuela,
OL,16,Fincluding British Red Cross, Oxfam and
OL,17,FSave the Children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
