OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FMore than 1,900 people have now been
OL,7,Fconfirmed dead with more than 40,000
OL,8,Fstill missing, since the powerful back-
OL,9,Fto-back earthquakes struck an area
OL,10,Fnear the capital Caracas on Wednesday
OL,11,F24 June.
OL,13,FAround 2,500 buildings are believed to
OL,14,Fhave been destroyed.
OL,16,FVenezuelan authorities have declared a
OL,17,Fstate of emergency and the UN
OL,18,Festimates that millions of people have
OL,19,Fbeen affected, with more than two
OL,20,Fmillion in the worst impacted areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FThe DEC described the scale of
OL,7,Fdestruction as "catastrophic".
OL,9,FDEC CEO Saleh Saeed said: "Thousands
OL,10,Fof people in Venezuela have survived
OL,11,Fthe unimaginable horror of two
OL,12,Fdevastating earthquakes only to face
OL,13,Fthe trauma of missing loved ones and
OL,14,Ffinding their homes and neighborhoods
OL,15,Fdestroyed.
OL,17,F"Right now, many of these families are
OL,18,Fsleeping in makeshift tents on the
OL,19,Fstreet. They urgently need shelter,
OL,20,Ffood, water, and medical care.
OL,26,@qD@[OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
