OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,F"DEC charities are working around the
OL,7,Fclock with their local partners to
OL,8,Freach people. The needs are
OL,9,Foverwhelming and the British public's
OL,10,Fsupport could be a lifeline for
OL,11,Ffamilies affected by this devastating
OL,12,Fdisaster. Please donate now."
OL,14,FITV News, as well as other UK
OL,15,Fbroadcasters, will air appeals on
OL,16,FWednesday evening, with BBC and
OL,17,Fcommercial radio appeals broadcast
OL,18,Fthroughout the day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
