PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FEvery pound donated by the British
OL,7,Fpublic will be matched by the UK
OL,8,Fgovernment through its UK Aid Match
OL,9,Fscheme, up to the value of #2 million.
OL,11,FDEC charities and their local partners
OL,12,Fhave been working in Venezuela for
OL,13,Fmany years, providing emergency
OL,14,Fmedical treatment, delivering food,
OL,15,Fand ensuring people have access to
OL,16,Fclean drinking water, but the DEC says
OL,17,Ffunds are urgently needed to reach
OL,18,Fmore families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
