CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FVenezuela was facing a severe economic
OL,7,Fcrisis before the earthquakes. Now
OL,8,Fhomes and businesses in Caracas and
OL,9,Facross several states have been
OL,10,Fdestroyed or damaged, with a
OL,11,Fparticularly serious impact reported
OL,12,Fin the La Guaira and Greater Caracas
OL,13,Fareas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FMany survivors are sleeping in
OL,7,Fmakeshift tents on the street and
OL,8,Furgently need shelter, food and water.
OL,9,FUN agencies have expressed concern
OL,10,Fabout the health effects of thousands
OL,11,Fof displaced people sleeping for days
OL,12,Fin the open or in crowded, unsanitary
OL,13,Fshelters.
OL,15,FWith road, power lines and critical
OL,16,Finfrastructure destroyed, families are
OL,17,Fcut off from essential services and
OL,18,Fsupplies, and the country's hospitals
OL,19,Fare under extreme pressure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
