FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782902882
OL,3,CDEC launches Venezuela earthquake
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,7,F"The earthquakes in Venezuela last
OL,8,Fweek have been devastating. Already we
OL,9,Fhave sent our UK search and rescue
OL,10,Fteam to help. But the people of
OL,11,FVenezuela desperately need urgent
OL,12,Fhumanitarian support from across the
OL,13,Fglobe.
OL,15,F"That is why the UK Government are
OL,16,Fmatching funding up to #2m of public
OL,17,Fdonations to DEC's appeal to provide
OL,18,Furgent humanitarian assistance, as
OL,19,Fpart of a wider package of support
OL,20,Ffrom the UK."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@MO]
